<br>
PoK is a &quot;safe are&quot; *obviously*<br>
<br>
All-Out Warfare<br>
<br>
You MUST keep channel /colorado up, but plan in /Guild<br>
<br>
If some major event occurs (Dragon, etc) war is suspended until raid is over<br>
<br>
Keep track of who you kill, we will have tallies<br>
<br>
Do NOT attack someone who is grouped for XP/Raid purposes<br>
<br>
Getting &quot;jumped&quot; by several people is legal<br>
<br>
Do NOT camp bind-points, give opponents time to loot corpse<br>
<br>
Anon/Invis/Items/Spells...EVERYTHING goes<br>
<br>
Be a good winner/loser, this is for fun folks<br>
<br>
Thats about it, oh, and HAVE FUN!<br>
